WEBVTT

00:00:07.437 --> 00:00:14.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Young man and young woman,
do give your heart to me.

00:00:14.062 --> 00:00:21.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
My foe who now taunts me
will then be made to see.

00:00:21.270 --> 00:00:28.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Your youth and devotion
to me you freely give;

00:00:28.729 --> 00:00:37.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You show all the world
that for me you really live.

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:44.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Beloved son
and precious daughter,

00:00:44.187 --> 00:00:51.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Be wise
and make my heart rejoice.

00:00:51.604 --> 00:00:57.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That out of your own heart
you serve me,

00:00:57.895 --> 00:01:05.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And furnish praise
by your own choice.

00:01:12.937 --> 00:01:20.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Rejoice and take pleasure
in giving me your all,

00:01:20.395 --> 00:01:27.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And though you may stumble,
I’ll raise you if you fall.

00:01:27.229 --> 00:01:34.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
No matter who fails you
or proves to be untrue,

00:01:34.229 --> 00:01:42.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Take comfort in knowing
I’ll always cherish you.

00:01:42.645 --> 00:01:50.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Beloved son
and precious daughter,

00:01:50.229 --> 00:01:57.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Be wise
and make my heart rejoice.

00:01:57.312 --> 00:02:03.937 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That out of your own heart
you serve me,

00:02:03.937 --> 00:02:12.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And furnish praise
by your own choice.

